先啦49000"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9cf3da30d2dccc003c5a030aecd11a299944a3","tid":1118494,"uid":143940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"周日英超賽事近況平平的曼聯將作客愛華頓，繼續為前4之位搶分，希望憑著對賽往績上的優勢在今仗贏波反彈。<br />\n<br />\n現時紅魔只比第3位的熱刺少3分兼少打一場，爭逐前4的機會仍然樂觀，但必須改善近期不穩的表現，尤其防守上已連績10仗失波，是近7年的第一次。<br />\n<br />\n事實上曼聯在周中歐聯作客巴塞隆拿輸波出局後，作客已連輸4場是1999年來的第一次。幸好球隊面對愛華頓向來佔盡上風，歷來英超交手已贏了36次，是聯賽最多紀錄，即使近9次交鋒亦有6勝2和1負。<br />\n<br />\n之前連贏3場的「拖肥糖」上仗作客竟不敵已篤定降班的富咸，表現令人失望。球隊今仗有中場安祖高美斯停賽缺陣，中堅耶利文拿亦因傷倦勤。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯方面則有左閘勞基梳爾停賽，但中場安達靴里拉已經復操，領隊蘇斯克查排陣或作出輪換。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=76220065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4958522923410e63a8e2ee2b7a95cedee386b7d8","tid":1118494,"uid":12682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wS6cv37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwS6cv37.png&h=4200ce8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b93a34930ebc7935fabfa8881228f2caa8a303","tid":1118494,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"𨳒你老母 <br />\n未買人解放博格巴咋<br />\n解放左使能輸？"},{"pid":"2f7abd9beb14ab8175fea4dcb5b0c29cb2c904fb","tid":1118494,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:05:25.000Z","msg":"迪閪亞勁到"},{"pid":"0fa1256be748db5bf9feb83bd1b6e893eef8b652","tid":1118494,"uid":64710,"li